00:00:35.060 --> 00:00:39.060
to see you all her for what is
going to be; I know is going

00:00:39.060 --> 00:00:43.280
to be a great, great program today.

00:00:43.280 --> 00:00:47.910
So, I'm going to say a few
things about our division.

00:00:47.910 --> 00:00:52.350
It is a division, which is
responsible for collections

00:00:52.350 --> 00:00:55.240
from 78 different countries.

00:00:55.240 --> 00:00:59.470
We're responsible for collections
for the whole continent of Africa,

00:00:59.470 --> 00:01:03.530 position:56%
Sub-Saharan Africa and North Africa.

00:01:03.530 --> 00:01:08.790
The whole Middle East, which
includes the Arab world, Turkey,

00:01:08.790 --> 00:01:15.120
Iran and also the whole of
Central Asia and the caucuses.

00:01:15.120 --> 00:01:22.170
Now -- and the third section of the
division is the Hebraic section,

00:01:22.170 --> 00:01:28.100
and we collect worldwide
for the Hebraic section;

00:01:28.100 --> 00:01:32.020
so that's quite a responsibility.

00:01:32.020 --> 00:01:36.170
We are 21 members of this division.

00:01:36.170 --> 00:01:45.090
And each of us has scholarly
publications, have written,

00:01:45.090 --> 00:01:49.860
have presented at conferences.

00:01:49.860 --> 00:01:55.190
Many have -- know several
languages and so the materials

