materials are to be found.

00:02:28.170 --> 00:02:30.800
We feel that this is
part of our work.

00:02:30.800 --> 00:02:34.930
We feel very responsible for
these materials and we want

00:02:34.930 --> 00:02:37.790 position:56%
to share them in every possible way.

00:02:37.790 --> 00:02:42.400
So we have this place, the
