00:20:32.510 --> 00:20:35.980
that we'll see with one
particular family in [Inaudible]

00:20:35.980 --> 00:20:41.200
and then I'll touch a little on
elite women and their predicament

00:20:41.200 --> 00:20:48.040
and what their fate
was in these scenarios.

00:20:48.040 --> 00:20:49.640
So when we look at
the interconnections

00:20:49.640 --> 00:20:53.010
at the imperial center,
one of the first things

00:20:53.010 --> 00:20:54.550
and most obvious things
you'll see is

00:20:54.550 --> 00:20:58.010
that the regional powers
start becoming interconnected

00:20:58.010 --> 00:20:59.780
