00:21:09.620 --> 00:21:11.430
Marriages were not full proof.

00:21:11.430 --> 00:21:14.140
Sometimes they worked,
sometimes they didn't.

00:21:14.140 --> 00:21:18.090
And that left mostly
women, not always,

00:21:18.090 --> 00:21:22.870
