difficulties of regional unrest

00:21:53.910 --> 00:21:57.180
and religious disagreements
as Tewodros.

00:21:57.180 --> 00:21:59.950
Three contenders to
the throne emerged.

00:21:59.950 --> 00:22:03.120
Pictured here Adal Tessema,
later Negus Takla Haimanot

00:22:03.120 --> 00:22:06.390
