to Yohannes, then Menilek.

00:22:27.070 --> 00:22:31.570
Between 1868 and 1889 even
while political maneuverings

00:22:31.570 --> 00:22:35.820
and conflict continued among these
and other figures less visible,

00:22:35.820 --> 00:22:38.990
but equally strategic
negotiations took place in the form

00:22:38.990 --> 00:22:44.140
