00:23:11.210 --> 00:23:14.700
of Giorgis and this provided a
diplomatic front between Shoa

00:23:14.700 --> 00:23:17.330
and Lasta and their
descendants continued

00:23:17.330 --> 00:23:20.620
to occupy important positions
into the 20th century

00:23:20.620 --> 00:23:23.340
in the families of Rascasa.

00:23:23.340 --> 00:23:26.930
So to give you a visual
idea of how this plays

00:23:26.930 --> 00:23:33.590
out we see here the three
sort of regional powers

00:23:33.590 --> 00:23:36.550
and Emperor Takla Giorgis family.

00:23:36.550 --> 00:23:41.670
Takla Giorgis appointed
Adal Ras in 1869,

00:23:41.670 --> 00:23:46.360
bestowing him with the governorship
of Gojjam, Damut and ago mandir.

00:23:46.360 --> 00:23:50.870
He also gave him his sister
[Inaudible] in marriage.

00:23:50.870 --> 00:23:53.870
While Takla Giorgis gamble
with Adal that worked out,

00:23:53.870 --> 00:23:55.430
appeared to be successful.

00:23:55.430 --> 00:24:00.280
He was soon faced with a more
serious threat from Casa,

00:24:00.280 --> 00:24:04.450
Takla Giorgis marriage to
Casa's only sister Dinkinesh,

00:24:04.450 --> 00:24:06.840
did not deter Casa's rebellion.

00:24:06.840 --> 00:24:08.570
After winning a decisive battle

00:24:08.570 --> 00:24:13.990
in 1871 Casa was crowned Emperor
Yohannes IV the following year

00:24:13.990 --> 00:24:16.370
and we'll say a little bit
more about this particular,

00:24:16.370 --> 00:24:18.710
what happened in this
situation for [Inaudible].

00:24:18.710 --> 00:24:24.220
These early marriage
arrangements tied together Lasta,

00:24:24.220 --> 00:24:25.920
Gojjam and briefly Tigre.

00:24:25.920 --> 00:24:28.920
Soon shifted directions
in the accordance

00:24:28.920 --> 00:24:32.750
to changing politics The final
