So he said to Yohannes "It's
only that the girl is to young

00:28:53.720 --> 00:28:57.030
for marriage or this would
not have displeased me".

00:28:57.030 --> 00:29:00.410
Yohannes was not deterred
reminding Menilek that the children

00:29:00.410 --> 00:29:04.430
