babies held in leather slings

00:29:08.480 --> 00:29:09.780
and carriers [Inaudible].

00:29:09.780 --> 00:29:14.830
The wedding would proceed,
so Menilek returned

00:29:14.830 --> 00:29:18.890
to [Inaudible] to prepare
for ceremony.

00:29:18.890 --> 00:29:20.230 position:56%
[Inaudible] now gives us a very kind

00:29:20.230 --> 00:29:23.360
